title: Vege Fast Food
typeOfFood: Vegan, Organic, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Croatian
description: Veggie fast food in the city center near green market. Makes vegetables, basmati rice, integral pasta, veggie burger, soya steak, tofu and seitan sandwiches, burrito, pancakes, fruit salad, juice, and ice tea. Open late Apr to Sep. Closes at 4pm out of peak season - please inform HappyCow of exat dates. Remains open until midnight on busy nights in high summer.
